                    <statement>
                        <p> Here is an exponential expression:  <m> \frac {x^{a} \cdot x^{b}}{x^{c}}</m>.</p>
                        <p><ol label="a.">
                          <li>
                            <p>Let <m>a > 0, b \lt 0,</m> and <m>c >0</m>.  Is it possible to come up with numbers for <m>a, b,</m> and <m>c</m> so that the exponential expression equals <m>x^{<var name="$exponent"/>}</m>?
